    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the critical VANOS system recently serviced and the subframe reinforced for long-term structural integrity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein B16 coilovers, enhancing the chassis's lateral grip without compromising the daily drivability. While the Alpine White finish shows minor road rash consistent with its mileage, the internals are dialed in. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment. A true driver\u2019s specification optimized for performance.",
