    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 in a sophisticated Atomic Silver finish. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in wonderful shape both mechanically and aesthetically. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though upon close inspection, you may find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel well, consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is exceptionally clean and strictly smoke-free; the seats are plush, with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, including the premium audio system, navigation, and heated/ventilated seats, function perfectly. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service record from the local dealership. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a brake pad replacement within the last 3,000 miles. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a quiet and comfortable ride. This is a turnkey luxury SUV ready for its next owner, offering a perfect balance of comfort and dependability.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
